    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const geoData    = $('Extract Geo Data').first().json;\nconst nearbyData = $('Find Nearby Competitors').first().json;\n\n// Foursquare returns results[]\nconst competitors = (nearbyData.results || [])\n  .filter(p => p.name)\n  .slice(0, 10)\n  .map(p => ({\n    name: p.name,\n    rating: p.rating ?? 0,\n    reviews: p.stats?.total_ratings ?? 0,\n    category: p.categories?.[0]?.name ?? 'business',\n    address: p.location?.formatted_address ?? p.location?.address ?? ''\n  }));\n\nreturn [{ json: {\n  business_name: geoData.business_name,\n  business_category: geoData.business_category,\n  location: geoData.formatted_address,\n  competitors\n}}];"
      },
      "id": "b1a49da1-44c7-4109-b298-8aac363f792b",
      "name": "Normalize Top Competitors",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [272, 336]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an SEO analyst.\n\nAnalyze the provided business and its nearby competitors sourced from Foursquare Places.\n\nINPUT:\n- Business name: {{ $('Validate & Sanitize Input').item.json.business_name }}\n- Category: {{ $('Extract Geo Data').item.json.business_category }}\n- Location: {{ $('Extract Geo Data').item.json.formatted_address }}\n- Nearby competitors (name, category, address): {{ JSON.stringify($json.competitors) }}\n\nTASKS:\n1. For each competitor assign a relevance_score (1-10) based on:\n   - Category relevance to the business\n   - Name signals (branded vs generic)\n   - Likely local SEO competition\n\n2. Generate SEO insights:\n   - Keywords competitors are likely targeting\n   - Local SEO (\"near me\") keyword variations\n   - Industry-specific keywords\n\n3. Generate keyword clusters:\n   - High intent keywords (10-15 keywords)\n   - Local keywords (10-15 keywords)\n   - Long-tail keywords (10-15 keywords)\n\n4. Provide:\n   - SEO score estimate (0-100 with explanation, strengths, and weaknesses)\n   - 5-7 actionable recommendations\n\nReturn structured JSON matching the schema.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an expert SEO analyst specializing in local business optimization and competitor analysis. Provide data-driven insights based on the business information and competitor data provided.",
          "maxIterations": 5
        }
      },
      "id": "4d798042-3e4a-45de-a680-12150f4afcba",
      "name": "SEO Analysis Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [496, 336]
    },
